# TITLE
Sketch App

# DESCRIPTION
Sketch app designed using HTML, CSS and JS

# FEATURES
- Different attractive colours for line with a suitable range of line weights
- Customizable background colour with auto-generated background on loading
- Clear screen or just erase your mistakes when needed.
- Supports both drawing horizontal and vertical lines.
- Rulers, both horizontal and vertical with a marker indicating the exact position of the cursor.
- Toggle feature to switch the rulers' dimensions unit from inches to centimetres and vice versa.
- Displays the exact position in the current unit.
- Save your sketch for later

# UPCOMING FEATURES
- Support for drawing diagonal lines.
- Improved UI/UX designs